all_reviews.review_content:
What do you like best about EngageBay All-in-One Suite?
- it's a great tool for marketing automation for small companies (finally!) and for a reasonable price;
- you can customize all views and see the data you want to;
- you can take a bulk action on multiple contacts - this makes work easier and faster (and if you work on another platform, you can easily transfer your contact list);
- it enables creating contact lists so you can send tailor-made content;
- fully customized forms are a great way to gather leads from your website;
- you can create a custom domain for landing pages built in EngageBay - it's very important to build credibility, cause people don't want to click on unknown links.


PS: I'm referring to the Marketing Platform mostly.

What do you dislike about EngageBay All-in-One Suite?
I don't find anything to dislike, this tool seems to be pretty helpful.

What problems is EngageBay All-in-One Suite solving and how is that benefiting you?
I can have all-in-one tool to control and manage all marketing actions.

